{"tid":847521,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"其實依架係咪多咗一type動漫 叫轉生類？","createTime":"2018-10-04T08:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T13:28:03.000Z","uid":90520,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"1a276523084fd9efc85483a4f3969f6b86953e34","tid":847521,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"呢兩年真係痴撚線<br />\n唔知由咩開始 就係咁出轉生類型嘅漫畫<br />\n全部嘅頭都一樣<br />\n有蜘蛛 有史萊姆 有魔法師(失格) 有哥布林<br />\n應該仲有一堆<br />\n不過 我齋有睇呢4個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一開頭係幾過癮嘅 不過呢type漫畫都好易估到後面<br />\n<br />\n或者大家有冇咩推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經典範例轉生漫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd7226f0267a67c7147f0c5825a8689c48ddb05","tid":847521,"uid":26506,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:37:23.000Z","msg":"大家都係穿越去異世界，唔使分得咁細"},{"pid":"bbbdc968e90d07a8d6fe328fe7fdb44f6fb110f9","tid":847521,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:38:10.000Z","msg":"沉悶"},{"pid":"95d6bdd293031bc907350cfd9b5f06420349bce6","tid":847521,"uid":69741,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:42:26.000Z","msg":"好耐啦都唔係呢兩年，轉生，異世界，主角好勁/好廢其實好勁，好多女<br />\n十套有九套都中一兩樣"},{"pid":"9e39129107be155b57c49f56c834cbd78849931c","tid":847521,"uid":5320,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"Re zero<br />\nKonosuba<br />\nOverlord"},{"pid":"bfe9269853c281cbe82690f12feeb59c1e801c70","tid":847521,"uid":147226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T08:57:11.000Z","msg":"上一浸熱潮（勇者/魔王）多到濫咗嘛，咪變咗呢一浸（轉生異世界）<br />\n<br />\n呢浸完咗又會變第二啲野"},{"pid":"a0e2501df3a67e9854c64bfe0510d09faecc51b4","tid":847521,"uid":12471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score